Fearure :  Test login and purchase

1. Scenario:Succesfull login
Given user Launch Chrome brouser
When user opens URL 'https://www.saucedemo.com/'
And user enters username as 'standard_user' and Password 'secret_sauce'
And user click on Login
Then products label is displayed
And close browser


2. Scenario Unsuccesfull login 
Given user Launch Chrome brouser 
When user opens URL 'https://www.saucedemo.com/'
And user enters username as 'wrong_user' and Password 'wrong_pass'
And user click on Login
Then a message indicating a wrong login should be displayed
And close browser

3. Scenario Successful Login and Purchase
Given user Launch Chrome brouser and adding some products
When user opens URL 'https://www.saucedemo.com/'
And user enters username as 'standard_user' and Password 'secret_sauce'
And user click on Login
Then products are displayed
And user add BikeLight,backpack,babybody
Then user check count in the cart
Then press cart button
And user should be redirected to Send page
And user enters their name adress and postal code
Then user clik on continue button
Then check count of the sum
And user click finish
And user should be redirected to page compleate order

